{
  "1772530": {
    "name": "玩具军团模拟器",
    "steam_appid": 1772530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/cca777d9d24bd10ef9bd0e0c092f1b7f.avif?t=1772021722\" width=600 height=129 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《玩具军团模拟器》中，你将化身传奇指挥官，挥动画笔在战场上自由绘制阵型布局。从楔形阵到各种天马行空的创意阵型，都能轻松实现——考验你想象力与战略思维的时刻到了！除了丰富刺激的单人战役模式，你还可以在 “1v1” 对战或合作模式中，与其他玩家对战或协作。现在就率领你的军团，踏上通往胜利的征途吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/df16d3574644789c64b19646bbf95ba1.poster.avif?t=1772021722\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/df16d3574644789c64b19646bbf95ba1.webm?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/df16d3574644789c64b19646bbf95ba1.mp4?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/f102cddd8c9657d1279e5f544f28251b.avif?t=1772021722\" width=700 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场，就是你的画布！在激烈的对抗中，你可以随时按下暂停，挥动画笔重新定义整支军队的阵型走向：从最基础的冲锋、包围，到更高阶的夹击、钳形攻势、楔形突进等战术，都由你一笔绘出。你还能将军队拆分为多个小队，为每支小队量身定制不同的阵型风格，让整个战场像一幅由你亲手编排的动态战术图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片残酷而壮阔的战场上，你就是最强的战术艺术家，挥洒你的画笔，让战局随你而动吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/0f4b33bb77c1f506fc71c202b404844f.poster.avif?t=1772021722\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/0f4b33bb77c1f506fc71c202b404844f.webm?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/0f4b33bb77c1f506fc71c202b404844f.mp4?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/25a1cc6f65bc1b84c3eabe3e1ae14085.avif?t=1772021722\" width=700 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《玩具军团模拟器》中，每一次碰撞、每一场混战，都进行了实时物理模拟。你的士兵在冲锋时头盔可能被打飞，木制陷阱会从高处滚落砸碎队形，城墙会在重击下崩塌成碎片，建筑在持续炮击后彻底垮塌。当战场被这些真实发生的事件完全淹没时，你能看到整片战场如同一场失控的风暴在眼前爆发，在这种瞬息万变的局势中，你能否根据实时反馈及时调整战术，扭转战局？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/52e35cad25a09ca6937dc5354b1c7071.poster.avif?t=1772021722\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/52e35cad25a09ca6937dc5354b1c7071.webm?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/52e35cad25a09ca6937dc5354b1c7071.mp4?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/4efc26c8234610166ba2e1de24d79b25.avif?t=1772021722\" width=700 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用法术与遗物系统，在最关键的时刻逆转战局！击败敌人即可积蓄能量：你可以召唤投石机增援、迅速搭建医疗帐篷为部队回血，或让燃烧的陨石从天而降，瞬间打击敌军士气。通过技能树解锁你最爱的法术，自由组合打造独一无二的战斗风格——策略组合无上限，你的每个想法都可能成为通往胜利的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/34423b0bb3cf1e6ae352173ab6377353.poster.avif?t=1772021722\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/34423b0bb3cf1e6ae352173ab6377353.webm?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/34423b0bb3cf1e6ae352173ab6377353.mp4?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/75dc9ee97505eddb01de427debf03aa3.avif?t=1772021722\" width=700 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的所有的兵种都来自微缩模型的启发——这些常用于重现历史战役或虚构世界的小模型，如今将真正走上战场！你将直面（或亲自指挥）骑着迅猛龙的骷髅战士、阴森的死灵法师、神出鬼没的武士，以及更多拥有独特能力的强大单位，这些对手嗜战如命，只为将你彻底击败。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/7174806bc056a0def429f5d264924a02.poster.avif?t=1772021722\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/7174806bc056a0def429f5d264924a02.webm?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772530/extras/7174806bc056a0def429f5d264924a02.mp4?t=1772021722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的征战旅程将跨越多个场景：从被加勒比海盗统治的托尔图加岛，到战国时代险峻的山峦，每处战场都充满惊喜与挑战——亲爱的指挥官，我们战场见！</p>",
